  m_Text: "\xA9 2018 in2sight GmbH. All rights reserved. game4automation\xAE is a
    registered trademark.\n\nrealvirtual.io (formerly game4automation) is a framework
    based on Unity to simplify automation design, 3d visualization of automation
    concepts and virtual commissioning. It is developed and maintained by in2sight
    GmbH. \n\nThis product bundles Sharp7,  Copyright (C) 2016 Davide Nardella. It
